Personality Quiz System
The quiz will consist of 6‚Äì8 simple multiple-choice questions to determine the user‚Äôs preferred companion personality and gender. The questions should be fun, quick, and reflective of the user‚Äôs personality or desires, mimicking the RPG vibe of Pok√©mon Mystery Dungeon (which uses questions to assign a Pok√©mon species) or Morrowind (which determines class and stats). The system will tally points for each personality and assign the one with the highest score.

Quiz Mechanics
Structure: Each question offers 4 answer choices, each subtly favoring one of the personalities (Sweet, Playful, Sultry, Goth). One question determines companion gender.
Scoring: Assign points (e.g., +1) to a personality for each answer. The personality with the most points at the end is selected.
Implementation: Use HTML for the quiz UI, JavaScript for scoring and logic, and localStorage to save the result. The chosen personality sets the initial system prompt for the Google chatbot API.
Replayability: Allow users to retake the quiz anytime via a ‚ÄúChange Companion‚Äù button, encouraging experimentation.
